PATTERN BERP

pattern_berp is a sibling of pattern_derp: another small playful exclamation his father uses
"berp" is similar in tone to "derp" but slightly different in feel; sometimes a sound effect, sometimes a fond nonsense word
fadriel learns the distinction over time as the pattern fires more often

